{"author":{"id":"cff9ab1d2ee9741039b2a60d90cca378a5320ba753398f6f3df8d03abcebee1b"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1771588921,"nonce":"/hq4sO+/bhsInM5LfV9lzy00VP0=","title":"Automatic anonymization of inactive staff users","message":"Staff user accounts (User model) have no automatic cleanup. When someone leaves the university, their account retains full personal data (name, email) indefinitely.\n\nNeed a scheduled job that anonymizes staff users who:\n- Have no active department memberships (all roles set to deleted), OR\n- Haven't logged in for a configurable period (e.g. 12 months)\n\nShould follow the same pattern as the existing borrower anonymization jobs (GdprAnonymizeInactiveBorrowersJob) and create GDPR audit log entries with nil performed_by.","files":null}]}